’Щ@46b87ba07887ce967ab9d710a2c57e8429ba1e6577d6a0759eaf6c3c3a28a044ЩЄTitle: title: path expand
Path: Flags
Content:
``--strict, -s``
: Throw an error if the path could not be expanded.
``--no-symlink, -n``
: Do not resolve symbolic links.
