’Щ@98259b4ad81bdab90a622fbc2e748142fb30d92dadfdd91fd36b42dfaf497e12ЪЙTitle: title: path expand
Path: Examples
Content:
Expand an absolute path.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> '/home/joe/foo/../bar' | path expand
/home/joe/bar

```
Expand a relative path.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> 'foo/../bar' | path expand


```
Expand a list of paths.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> [ /foo/../bar, /foo/../baz ] | path expand
в•­в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”¬в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв•®
в”‚ 0 в”‚ /bar в”‚
в”‚ 1 в”‚ /baz в”‚
в•°в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”ґв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв•Ї


```
